rules_text:
Whenever a creature dealt combat damage this turn by equipped creature dies, put a hand counter on Bag of Hands.
As long as there are five or more hand counters on Bag of Hands, equipped creature has “Whenever this creature blocks or becomes blocked, wound each creature blocking or being blocked by this creature.” [i](Until the end of your next turn, if a wounded creature would be dealt damage, it’s dealt that much damage plus one instead.)[/i]
Equip {1}
